The life path we create shapes our essence, defining what we have been and what we will be.
Moon Attraction' has a double meaning:
I wanted to represent the Moon that creates itself out of nothing by attracting the gaze of humanity towards itself, at the same time each of us can identify with it by attracting positive thoughts.
There is nothing more important than life.
